data.description: WELCOME TO YOUR 3 bedroom 3 bathroom + a Den + a Loft FARMHOUSE! Enter into foyer with vaulted ceilings. Then head into the great room and enjoy the open concept. The kitchen features granite countertops, subway tiled backsplash, stainless steel appliances, a pantry and an island. You can also enjoy BBQing on the backyard deck just steps away from the kitchen. The backyard is low maintenance with turf too. Downstairs features a den that could be used as an office for even a bedroom (there’s just no closet) The downstairs laundry room features extra shelving and subway tiles too! Head upstairs where you will find 3 bedrooms and 2 bathroom plus the loft. The primary bedroom features an oversized custom walk-in closet, a “pinterest perfect” bathroom featuring dual sinks, separate walk-in shower and tub too. The secondary bedrooms feature a walk-in closet and a shiplap wall. Turn this house into your home for the holidays! Don't miss out!
